  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Ama Ghar Community Earthquake Relief</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Ama Ghar is a home for orphaned and abandoned children about 16 kilometers outside Kathmandu. Because our home is well built and we live in the country, our children are temporarily safe and have enough food for 4 weeks, or until mid-May. Who knows what will happen after that? Our local schools are rubble and our neighbors are in need. We are the anchor of our small village and will use the funding for relief efforts for our children and surrounding village. Thank you for your generosity.</narrative>
  </description>
